               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist and of the angel Gäbrǝʾel (fol. 35va); names of the donors (often erased and overwritten with another name); elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
&#xD;
A few lines in the incipit of Texts I-1 and I-2 (alternating with black lines); one up to three lines in the incipit of sections of Text II (sometimes alternating with black lines).</rubric>
